    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一辆玩具小车能成为电子游戏的主角吗？某个夜晚，它的主人神秘失踪，杳无踪迹。被独自留在寂静房间里的这辆小车，踏上了一段诡异而神秘的旅程——去寻找那个男孩……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/84c5e49a55c677c2782670fd4d871f03.poster.avif?t=1771953070\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/84c5e49a55c677c2782670fd4d871f03.webm?t=1771953070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/84c5e49a55c677c2782670fd4d871f03.mp4?t=1771953070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为玩家，你将操控这辆玩具小车，解开巧妙的谜题，应对棘手的挑战，并设法逃离男孩的家。但旅程并未止步于此——小车还将驶出房屋，前往雾气弥漫的街道、废弃的场所，以及其他众多幽暗而氛围感十足的地点，一路追寻男孩神秘失踪的线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/a124686b0554b0470d44a39bea8f97cd.poster.avif?t=1771953070\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/a124686b0554b0470d44a39bea8f97cd.webm?t=1771953070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/a124686b0554b0470d44a39bea8f97cd.mp4?t=1771953070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对外面广阔的世界而言，一辆小小的玩具车可谓危机四伏：从高处坠落、火焰和水，都只是你将面对的部分危险。此外还有敌人——狗、扫地机器人，以及阴森可怖的玩具怪物，都会挡在你的去路。但别担心！得益于游戏的动态物理系统，你几乎可以推动、移动并与任何物体互动，从而为每个障碍找到富有创意的解决方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/4f8b7206a173d5a81062ed5a285279fa.poster.avif?t=1771953070\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/4f8b7206a173d5a81062ed5a285279fa.webm?t=1771953070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273260/extras/4f8b7206a173d5a81062ed5a285279fa.mp4?t=1771953070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场惊险刺激的冒险之旅，融合了诡异、温情与动人的情感时刻，适合全家一同体验。揭开男孩失踪背后的骇人谜团——也许他比你想象中更需要你的帮助！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即加入愿望单，不要错过正式发售！</p>",
